_:N421e8e8ccb35486cb43a2cd1e99873ad <http://schema.org/description> "The Civil Nuclear Police Authority oversees the Civil Nuclear Constabulary (CNC) and must ensure that their policing meets the need of the nuclear operating companies. CNPA is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Energy Security and Net Zero ." .
